This falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP) and computational linguistics (CL), which is covered by cs.CL. The use of logic and abductive inference also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (LG). Additionally, the paper's focus on temporal information extraction could also be relevant to the sub-categories of computer vision (CC) and cryptography and security (CR), as these fields often deal with analyzing and interpreting temporal data.
